Thank you for review. Do you mean JDK11 is slower? Here, JDK8 took more time. The following is the JDK8 result in this PR. JDK11 took `572.0ns` per row while JDK8 did `608.0ns` per row.
```
SerializationUtils.clone                              0              0           0          0.1       13640.0       1.0X
Utils.cloneProperties                                 0              0           0          1.6         608.0      22.4X
```
